column2: Tree Species List for the Monitoring Site 1000 Project
name_jp: Japanese name used in moni1000 sites
name_jp_std: Japanese name according to GreenList/YList
name_greenlist: scientific name according to GreenList/YList
match_type: match type in GBIF search
status: taxonomic status of the scientific name query in GBIF
species: species name includes the ranks of subspecies, variety and forma
species_jp: species name in Japanese (standard name)
categ: 1, Conifer excluding Abies and Tsuga; 2, Abies; 3, Tsuga; 4, Broadleaf
categ3: 1, formal japanese species name; 0, synonym in japanese
categ4: 1, Conifer; 2, Abies; 3, Tsuga; 4, Deciduous broadleaf; 5, Evergreen broadleaf. (use for a tree biomass estimation with allometric equations)
categ5: 1, Conifer; 4, Deciduous broadleaf; 5, Evergreen broadleaf
categ6: 1, Sub-boreal conifer; 2, Temperate conifer; 4, Deciduous broadleaf; 5, Evergreen broadleaf
